### Per-package lockfiles ###
# Per-package lockfiles aren't authoritative in npm workspaces; only the
# root package-lock.json is. Delete any that get accidentally created.
/service.backend/package-lock.json
/app.*/package-lock.json
/lib.*/package-lock.json

